        "title": [
          {
            "type": "Text",
            "text": "/unfreeze — Clear Freeze Boundary"
          }
        ],
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "Text",
            "text": "<!-- AUTO-GENERATED from SKILL.md.tmpl — do not edit directly -->\n<!-- Regenerate: bun run gen:skill-docs -->\n\n\nRemove the edit restriction set by `/freeze`, allowing edits to all directories.\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.gstack/analytics\necho '{\"skill\":\"unfreeze\",\"ts\":\"'$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)'\",\"repo\":\"'$(basename \"$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel 2>/dev/null)\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"unknown\")'\"}'  >> ~/.gstack/analytics/skill-usage.jsonl 2>/dev/null || true\n```"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "kind": {
              "type": "Section",
              "attrs": {
                "id": null,
                "pairs": {}
              },
              "title": [
                {
                  "type": "Text",
                  "text": "Clear the boundary"
                }
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "kind": {
                    "type": "Paragraph",
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "text": "```bash\nSTATE_DIR=\"${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_DATA:-$HOME/.gstack}\"\nif [ -f \"$STATE_DIR/freeze-dir.txt\" ]; then\n  PREV=$(cat \"$STATE_DIR/freeze-dir.txt\")\n  rm -f \"$STATE_DIR/freeze-dir.txt\"\n  echo \"Freeze boundary cleared (was: $PREV). Edits are now allowed everywhere.\"\nelse\n  echo \"No freeze boundary was set.\"\nfi\n```\n\nTell the user the result. Note that `/freeze` hooks are still registered for the\nsession — they will just allow everything since no state file exists. To re-freeze,\nrun `/freeze` again."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "span": {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 0
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            "span": {
              "start": 0,
              "end": 0
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "span": {
        "start": 0,
        "end": 0
      }
    }
  ]
